InnerGold Counseling Services provides assistance to individuals 
struggling with pornography and sexual addictions, as well as, 
help for their family members.
Gordon S. Bruin, M.A, L.P.C, president and founder of 
InnerGold Counseling Services Inc., is an American Board 
Certified, Licensed Professional Counselor specializing in 
addictions counseling. He received his Master of Arts degree 
in Clinical Psychology from John. F. Kennedy University, with 
a specialization in addiction studies. He has spent many years 
and countless hours helping those struggling with pornography/
sexual addiction issues and is a known expert in the field. He has 
lectured and provided trainings and consultation to numerous 
community, religious, and professional organizations.
